reviewText: Item as described and shipped promptly Recommend to all
Eddie "Funny" Murphy at his best.  Trading Places and 48 Hours are classic R-rated comedies that you will love!
Come on Trading places is one the best movie of all time
Love all these movies now so glad I have them on blu ray
I got this purely for 48 Hours and Trading Places, so Norbit was a bonus for me. Two of Eddie Murphy's best ever films.

I rate cause I like Eddie Murphy. I watched all 3 triple feature movies On this blu-ray disc. Trading Places and Norbit come with special features. And 48 H.R.S. only comes with a trailer. No problem with any of these movies. I would recommend this to a friend or family member.
I love Eddie Murphy movies and these three are not an exception so happy I was able to find it in a combo pack.
